### 7. `Components/Layout/MainLayout.razor` — embed the interactive islands

Replace the top-row div to include `ThemeIndicator` and `ThemeToggle`:

```razor
@inherits LayoutComponentBase

<div class="page">
    <div class="sidebar">
        <NavMenu />
    </div>

    <main>
        <div class="top-row px-4">
            <ThemeIndicator />
            <ThemeToggle />
            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core/" target="_blank">About</a>
        </div>

        <article class="content px-4">
            @Body
        </article>
    </main>
</div>

<div id="blazor-error-ui" data-nosnippet>
